# Modelo de Datos — Metrolinea (PostgreSQL)

## Infraestructura

### `stations`
| Campo   | Tipo    | Notas                  |
|---------|---------|------------------------|
| id      | serial  | PK                     |
| code    | varchar | Ej: EST-01             |
| name    | varchar |                        |
| address | varchar |                        |
| lat     | numeric |                        |
| lng     | numeric |                        |

### `routes`
| Campo       | Tipo    | Notas                        |
|-------------|---------|------------------------------|
| id          | serial  | PK                           |
| code        | varchar | Ej: P2                       |
| name        | varchar |                              |
| description | text    |                              |
| status      | varchar | active / inactive            |

### `route_stations`
Paradas ordenadas de cada ruta.

| Campo                       | Tipo    | Notas                              |
|-----------------------------|---------|------------------------------------|
| id                          | serial  | PK                                 |
| route_id                    | int     | FK → routes                        |
| station_id                  | int     | FK → stations                      |
| stop_order                  | int     | Orden dentro de la ruta            |
| estimated_minutes_from_prev | int     | Tiempo estimado desde parada previa|

### `buses`
| Campo         | Tipo    | Notas                              |
|---------------|---------|------------------------------------|
| id            | serial  | PK                                 |
| code          | varchar | Ej: 003                            |
| license_plate | varchar |                                    |
| capacity      | int     | Máximo de pasajeros                |
| status        | varchar | active / inactive / maintenance    |

---

## Programación

### `schedule_templates`
Plantilla maestra de la que se generan los viajes diarios.

| Campo              | Tipo    | Notas                                      |
|--------------------|---------|--------------------------------------------|
| id                 | serial  | PK                                         |
| route_id           | int     | FK → routes                                |
| departure_time     | time    | Hora de salida desde primera estación      |
| frequency_minutes  | int     | Intervalo entre salidas                    |
| days_of_week       | int[]   | Ej: [1,2,3,4,5] (lunes a viernes)          |
| valid_from         | date    |                                            |
| valid_until        | date    |                                            |

### `daily_trips`
Viajes concretos generados a partir del template para un día específico.

| Campo               | Tipo      | Notas                                                        |
|---------------------|-----------|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| id                  | serial    | PK                                                           |
| route_id            | int       | FK → routes                                                  |
| bus_id              | int       | FK → buses                                                   |
| date                | date      |                                                              |
| scheduled_departure | timestamp | Salida programada desde primera estación                     |
| status              | varchar   | scheduled / in_progress / completed / cancelled / delayed    |

### `trip_stops`
Paso del viaje por cada estación (puntualidad por parada).

| Campo               | Tipo      | Notas                     |
|---------------------|-----------|---------------------------|
| id                  | serial    | PK                        |
| daily_trip_id       | int       | FK → daily_trips          |
| station_id          | int       | FK → stations             |
| stop_order          | int       |                           |
| scheduled_arrival   | timestamp |                           |
| actual_arrival      | timestamp | Nullable                  |
| scheduled_departure | timestamp |                           |
| actual_departure    | timestamp | Nullable                  |

---

## Usuarios y demanda

### `users`
| Campo         | Tipo    | Notas                          |
|---------------|---------|--------------------------------|
| id            | serial  | PK                             |
| name          | varchar |                                |
| email         | varchar | Unique                         |
| password_hash | varchar |                                |
| role          | varchar | admin / operator / passenger   |
| created_at    | timestamp |                              |

### `trip_plans`
Trayectos que el pasajero registrado agenda con antelación.

| Campo              | Tipo      | Notas                                    |
|--------------------|-----------|------------------------------------------|
| id                 | serial    | PK                                       |
| user_id            | int       | FK → users                               |
| route_id           | int       | FK → routes                              |
| origin_station_id  | int       | FK → stations                            |
| dest_station_id    | int       | FK → stations                            |
| planned_date       | date      |                                          |
| planned_time       | time      |                                          |
| status             | varchar   | active / cancelled / completed           |

### `user_trip_assignments`
Asignación concreta de un usuario a un `daily_trip` (resultado de un patch aprobado).

| Campo         | Tipo    | Notas                         |
|---------------|---------|-------------------------------|
| id            | serial  | PK                            |
| trip_plan_id  | int     | FK → trip_plans               |
| daily_trip_id | int     | FK → daily_trips              |
| status        | varchar | assigned / boarded / missed   |

---

## Logs en tiempo real

### `journey_logs`
Datos de la cámara del bus (ocupación durante el trayecto).

| Campo         | Tipo      | Notas                          |
|---------------|-----------|--------------------------------|
| id            | serial    | PK                             |
| daily_trip_id | int       | FK → daily_trips               |
| timestamp     | timestamp |                                |
| passenger_count | int     |                                |
| event_type    | varchar   | periodic / change              |

### `station_events`
Datos del sensor de estación (llegada y salida del bus).

| Campo         | Tipo      | Notas                          |
|---------------|-----------|--------------------------------|
| id            | serial    | PK                             |
| daily_trip_id | int       | FK → daily_trips               |
| station_id    | int       | FK → stations                  |
| event_type    | varchar   | arrival / departure            |
| timestamp     | timestamp |                                |
| passenger_count | int     | Conteo en el momento del evento|

---

## IA

### `ai_triggers`
Eventos que activan la evaluación del agente IA.

| Campo         | Tipo      | Notas                                                              |
|---------------|-----------|--------------------------------------------------------------------|
| id            | serial    | PK                                                                 |
| trigger_type  | varchar   | pre_day_evaluation / low_occupancy / bus_full / high_demand        |
| route_id      | int       | FK → routes (nullable)                                             |
| daily_trip_id | int       | FK → daily_trips (nullable)                                        |
| payload       | jsonb     | Contexto adicional para el agente                                  |
| status        | varchar   | pending / processing / resolved                                    |
| created_at    | timestamp |                                                                    |

### `ai_patches`
Propuestas de acción generadas por el agente IA, pendientes de aprobación del operador.

| Campo            | Tipo      | Notas                                                  |
|------------------|-----------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| id               | serial    | PK                                                     |
| trigger_id       | int       | FK → ai_triggers                                       |
| analysis         | text      | Razonamiento del agente                                |
| proposed_actions | jsonb     | Array de acciones propuestas                           |
| status           | varchar   | pending / approved / modified / rejected               |
| reviewed_by      | int       | FK → users (operador)                                  |
| reviewed_at      | timestamp |                                                        |
| applied_at       | timestamp |                                                        |

---

## Sesiones de asistente (diferido)

### `assistant_sessions`
| Campo      | Tipo      | Notas              |
|------------|-----------|--------------------|
| id         | serial    | PK                 |
| user_id    | int       | FK → users         |
| started_at | timestamp |                    |
| ended_at   | timestamp | Nullable           |
| context    | jsonb     | Estado de sesión   |

### `assistant_messages`
| Campo      | Tipo      | Notas                  |
|------------|-----------|------------------------|
| id         | serial    | PK                     |
| session_id | int       | FK → assistant_sessions|
| role       | varchar   | user / assistant       |
| content    | text      |                        |
| created_at | timestamp |                        |
